{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT in other fieldsIn taking the American Heart Association's Basic Life Support and Advanced Cardiovascular Life Support examinations, ChatGPT did not reach a passing threshold.",
    "However, researchers noted that the answers provided by ChatGPT did not simply answer the question but also provided insightful explanations, regardless of whether the answer was correct or incorrect [19].",
    "This was further seen in a query project done in the field of Obstetrics and Gynecology by Grünebaum et al. [7] Although its answers were mostly on target, its responses to queries were \"nuanced, eloquent, informed, and had virtually no grammatical errors\" [7].",
    "We also found that despite no prompting by the input, ChatGPT provided explanations as to how it arrived at its answer choice.",
    "Only 14 out of 360 questions provided no logic (CN, IN), comprising roughly 3.9% of the dataset."
  ]
}